com.vmware.nsx_policy

Class NsxPolicyFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.NsxPolicyFactory

  • public class NsxPolicyFactory
extends Object
    NsxPolicyFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
